{"tid":2171580,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"雖然呢個運動唔捉鬼，但係今次我真係要捉鬼","createTime":"2020-08-24T04:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T04:57:37.000Z","uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"be1c2eb876f889acc15eb428f3538e1af9aac3b3","tid":2171580,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:56:04.000Z","msg":"點解美國囉宣布埋啲唔等駛嘅要求我哋中國香港要滿足配合佢？<br />\n<br />\n貿易係互惠互利 香港作為美國最大嘅貿易順差夥伴 美國要拎石頭摘自己嘅腳 點解港府要縮<br />\n<br />\n我宣佈邱騰華真係美國派嚟嘅人<br />\n<br />\n不斷出賣中國香港 同埋 佢啲手足 (林鄭 大波驊) 去做鬼 換美帝唔制裁<br />\n<br />\n【邱騰華：港產品須標中國製延至11.9落實】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3lgrqAK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3lgrqAK&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=aeceb9b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3lgrqAK</a><br />\n<br />\n美國要求在香港生產的商品出口到美國，不可以再貼出「#香港製造」標籤。商務及經濟發展局局長 #邱騰華 在一個網上研討會表示，該項政策實施日期延後45日，至11月9日才落實。<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------<br />\n信報<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFZ8iyo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFZ8iyo.jpg&h=a8bc1c3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"16306f1e5b5eed032d908c5b9d2034fe022dcfb7","tid":2171580,"uid":292343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T04:57:37.000Z","msg":"邱騰華係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}